me.kewi.api

Class PlayerRemoveTagEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.event.Event
      • me.kewi.api.PlayerRemoveTagEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cancellable

    public class PlayerRemoveTagEvent
extends Event
implements Cancellable

    Remove player team

    When player quit or is kicked, this is called to remove the player team. If player re-join in server, PlayerSetTagEvent is called to set new team to player.
